threads.title: A1534 820-00244-A don't work no image or DFU
threads.message:
i have this board :

PPBUS_G3H = 8,64v
PPBUS_S5_HS_COMPUTING_ISNS = 8,64V
PPVBUS_LIO = 20V
PP3V3R3V0_AON = 3,26V
PPVRTC_G3H = 3,05V
PP5V_G3H = 5v change 0v again 5v 1-2seconds
PP5V_S0 = 0V
PP3V3_S5 = 0V
PP3V3_S0 = 0V
PP3V3_SUS = 0V

any ideas? very thx !!

threads.title: A1534 820-00244-A don't work no image or DFU
threads.message:
Check U7800's LDOs voltage (page 46).
If any missing, check in diode mode too.
